    "description": "Aladdin eToken NG-FLASH (Java) and Aladdin eToken NG-OTP (Java) offer strong authentication and guaranteed non-repudiation for sensitive applications such as eBanking, stock trading, eCommerce and financial transactions. The modules are based on the Athena IDProtect Java Card smart card operating system that is compliant with the Java Card 2.2.2 and GlobalPlatform 2.1.1 specifications and FIPS 140-2 Level 3 (Level 4 for physical security). IDProtect supports FIPS Approved Random Number Generation, TDES, AES, SHA-1, SHA-256, and RSA up to 2048 bits including on board key generation.",
